00:35:12.310 --> 00:35:15.200
And do sum over all.

00:35:15.200 --> 00:35:20.320
So therefore, when you use this
formula for the line strings,

00:35:20.320 --> 00:35:26.910
whether you have the
situation on the left side

00:35:26.910 --> 00:35:35.610
