the e to the i omega t term,

00:44:37.320 --> 00:44:43.220
you would now find
operators a and dagger.

00:44:43.220 --> 00:44:47.220
But they would have factors
of i in front of it.

00:44:47.220 --> 00:44:50.810
That's a equation we
had when we derived it.

00:44:50.810 --> 00:44:56.220
Well I prefer note to use
