01:00:04.520 --> 01:00:08.190
The way how vacuum fluctuations
create a lamb shift or the way

01:00:08.190 --> 01:00:12.150
how vacuum fluctuations affect
an atom in the excited state,

01:00:12.150 --> 01:00:14.460
everything is included in here.

01:00:14.460 --> 01:00:16.820
The question is just
can we solve it.

01:00:16.820 --> 01:00:19.260
And the calculations
can get involved.

01:00:19.260 --> 01:00:23.280
